songs.title: ​giles corey
songs.lyrics:
based on instagram snippet

[Verse 1]
I feel the pressure
Weighing on my chest like a boulder
I built a casket
Carried it and broke the bones in my shoulders
Wish I could tell you
Everything I feel but I'm breathless
And this will kill me
I just wanted you to know I never meant this

Spring sky, I hide inside, I
Old times, new lies, alive again
I'd rather hurt myself than hurt someone else
I'd rather sink on my own than ask for help
I'd rather hurt myself than hurt someone else
I'd rather sink on my own than ever ask for help
